==English==

===Pronunciation===
* ''[[RP]]:'' {{IPA|/rɪˈspɒns/}}
* {{audio|en-us-response.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun-reg}}
# An [[answer]] or [[reply]], or something in the nature of an answer or reply.
# The act of [[respond]]ing or replying; reply: as, to speak in response to a question.
# An [[oracular]] answer.
# (''liturgics'') A [[verse]], sentence, phrase, or word said or sung by the [[choir]] or [[congregation]] in sequence or reply to the [[priest]] or [[officiant]].
# (''liturgics'') A [[versicle]] or [[anthem]] said or sung during or after a [[lection]]; a [[respond]] or [[responsory]].
# A reply to an [[objection]] in formal [[disputation]].

